  <p><font face="verdana" size="2"><a name="5"><font color="gold"><b>Fletching</b></font></a> 
    </font>
  <blockquote><font face="verdana" size="2">Fletching is a skill that takes time, 
    money and most of all patience. If you are interested in becoming a master 
    Fletcher I would suggest being a Ranger, Paladin, Warrior, Rogue or Shadowknight 
    else the skill isn't much use unless for profit. The skill you will find is 
    much more helpful then just creating profit for your character, if he/she 
    is one of these four classes.</font> 
